  "raw_text": "188\nजातकपारिजाते\nAdh I\n* Also फलदीपिका\nचान्द्रे रूपं श्लोक शूरो वरशः कुब्जे चित्रं भाग्यं श्लोके सुखामाम् ।\n26 12 13 25 24 11 26 14 13 25\nमैने राज्यं मृत्युभागाः प्रदिष्टाः मेषादीनां वर्गसख्यैर्हिर्माशोः ॥\n5 12\nThe (मृत्युभागाः) Mrityubhagas of the other planets and of the\nRasis in general as stated in other works have been collected and\ngiven in the following statement for easy reference:\nMrityu bhagas or fateful degrees of\nIn the Rasi mentioned hereunder\nSun. Mars. Mercury. Jupiter. Venus. Saturn. Rahu. Ketu. Mandi. Rasi.\nMesha 20 19 15 19 28 10 14 8 23 1\nVrishabha 9 28 14 29 15 4 13 18 24 9\nMithuna 12 25 13 12 11 7 12 20 11 22\nKataka 6 23 12 27 17 9 11 10 12 22\nSimha 8 29 8 6 10 12 24 21 13 25\nKanya 24 28 18 4 13 16 23 22 14 2\nThula 16 14 20 13 4 3 22 23 8 4\nVrischika 17 21 10 10 6 18 21 24 18 23\nDhanus 22 2 21 17 27 28 10 11 20 18\nMakara 2 15 22 11 12 14 20 12 10 20\nKumbha 3 11 7 15 29 13 18 13 21 24\nMeena 23 6 5 28 19 15 8 14 22 10",
